{"id":167727,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011718/","date":"2011-07-19T10:00:17Z","modified":"2011-07-19T10:00:17Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/7/18","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/19/world/asia/19china.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新疆派出所遭袭，至少四人死亡</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据境外维吾尔人组织称，当时有</span><span>100</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多人前往派出所抗议维族青年被抓。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/may/23/wang-keqin-china-investigative-journalism\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">王克勤与中国的调查报道革命</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“黑社会跟我过不去，红社会也跟我过不去。我听说有人专门在调查我，想把我送进监狱”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/jul/18/wang-keqin-journalist-china-fears\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">暗语留言令人担心中国记者的调查团队</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——王克勤的博客引起警觉，有消息称官员们要对中国经济时报的记者下手</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/jul/16/barack-obama-dalai-lama-white-house\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">奥巴马与达赖喇嘛见面</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在</span><span>45</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">分钟的见面期间，奥巴马重申保护中国藏人人权的重要性美联社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110717/ap_on_re_as/as_china_dalai_lama\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国抨击奥巴马与达赖喇嘛的见面</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“粗暴干涉了中国内政，伤害了中国人民的感情，破坏了中美关系”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/19/opinion/19iht-edli19.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">反击关于中国的一些误区</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“西方媒体对中国有五种主要的误解，它们需要以事实来加以澄清”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/gordonchang/2011/07/17/how-do-you-hide-an-oil-spill-ask-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">怎样瞒住石油泄漏事故？问中国吧</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据说康菲公司在漏油发生当天就通报了中方，但是中海油的对外通报在四个星期后才发生</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eastasiaforum.org/2011/07/16/tracing-the-limits-to-the-judicialisation-of-land-disputes-in-socialist-asia/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲社会主义国家土地纠纷的司法化</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——土地纠纷通过司法解决是世界趋势。但是在社会主义国家，由于司法不独立，这种手段很可能不是最佳解决手段</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8645405/Chinas-sport-scandals.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的体育丑闻</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国官员近年来不断受到批评，因为他们过于逼迫运动员，或把不到年龄的运动员推上赛场</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/17/world/asia/17music.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">少数民族音乐考验中国的限度</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的少数民族乐手们都明白，在歌词里、在表演时，都不要跟政治沾上边。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>CNN</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/07/16/china.rape.case/index.html?eref=edition_asia&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+rss%2Fedition_asia+%28RSS%3A+Asia%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国警方对一起强奸案的处理引起群情激愤</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“戴套就不算强奸”的说法受到网民无情嘲讽和愤怒指责</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/07/16/china-and-the-kachin-conflict/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国与克钦冲突</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——有人责怪是中国的水坝建设工程引起了缅甸克钦骚乱，而实际上事情远比这复杂</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/07/17/america%E2%80%99s-%E2%80%98munich-moment%E2%80%99/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国的“慕尼黑协定”时刻？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国在南海问题上对于中国的迁就，几乎就是二战前绥靖政策的翻版。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《美国新闻》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.usnews.com/news/articles/2011/07/15/debt-fight-reinforces-chinas-negative-views-of-america\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于债务上限的争执，加重了中国对美国的负面看法</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国衰落，中国崛起的印象被进一步加强</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《菲律宾每日问讯报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://newsinfo.inquirer.net/24146/china-will-become-%E2%80%98ruthless-monster%E2%80%99-says-indon-expert\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印尼专家称中国将成为“无情的魔鬼</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”——印尼大学教授称中国的目标是到</span><span>2020</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">成为霸权，并在东南亚地区挑起冲突</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《野兽日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2011/07/16/spies-from-china-use-the-internet-to-exploit-weaknesses-in-u-s.html?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+thedailybeast%2Farticles+%28The+Daily+Beast+-+Latest+Articles%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国面临中国的间谍浪潮</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——国防部官员正在努力计划抵御来自北京的网络攻击，同时还要应付大量的中国间谍</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《连线》杂志：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/2011/07/darpa-wants-social-media-sensor-for-propaganda-ops/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+WiredDangerRoom+%28Blog+-+Danger+Room%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">五角大楼想要建立社交媒体宣传机器</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——社交媒体的兴起也引起美国和北约军方的关注，他们在琢磨如何利用这一趋势。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/07/18/why-china-wants-the-south-china-sea/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么中国想要南海</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——那里不仅关系到中国的能源和渔业资源，而且也关系到中国的核潜艇战略</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/china-rich-with-coal-seeks-more-next-door-in-mongolia-to-meet-its-energy-needs/2011/07/01/gIQADIncII_story.html?hpid=z3\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">尽管中国煤炭丰富，但仍然与外蒙接触，寻求满足能源需要</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——北京眼里的供需关系，却可能引起复杂与危险的政治热情和对立情绪</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《印度时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-07-16/china/29781227_1_chinese-workers-chinese-leaders-state-councilor-dai-bingguo\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国告诫印度，在寻求安理会常任理事国问题上，不要与日本联手申请</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">半岛新闻：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.aljazeera.net/asia/2011/07/16/lumbini-project-chinas-3bn-buddhism\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">伦比尼工程：中国的</span>30<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元佛教奉献</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国计划在尼泊尔的释迦牟尼故乡投资</span><span>30</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元开发旅游资源，而这几乎相当于尼泊尔的全年</span><span>GDP</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律博客：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinalawblog.com/2011/07/who_owns_the_chinese_internet_who_cares.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">谁拥有中国的互联网？为什么要问这个问题？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——找出中国互联网公司的拥有者不是一件容易的事情</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2011/07/understanding-beijings-industrial-policy-for-the-21st-century/242036/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">了解北京的</span>21<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">世纪产业政策</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的稀土和有色金属出口限制要与其国内对高科技产业的鼓励结合起来看待</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110718/bs_nm/us_china_accounting_fitch\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">针对中国公司的指控还将继续</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——惠誉评级机构称针对中国上市公司有欺诈行为的指控在近期内还会延续下去</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲哨兵：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3326&#038;Itemid=208\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对自己的建坝研究报告置之不理</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国电力投资公司的评估报告称缅甸大坝不应建设</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110718/bs_nm/us_china_banks\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的大银行不会受地方债务影响</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——四大国有银行已陆续增加了坏账保证金。至少在账面上看起来，它们比较安全</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">成都加油：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.gochengdoo.com/en/blog/item/2311/graffiti_goes_local_a_tagger_without_borders_sack\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">成都本地的涂鸦艺术家</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【图说】——成都大约有</span><span>20</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名涂鸦艺术家。这是对其中一位的专访。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/18/movies/in-china-no-harry-potter-until-revolutionary-epic-is-a-hit.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">想看哈利波特，结果看的是建党伟业</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“就算控制整个影院系统，极力鼓励人们去看宣传片，但人们最终还是会只看自己想看的电影”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：您可以到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>看到推友们对该篇译文的评论和转发；欢迎参与！如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-1243970072718889817?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":665,"categories":[1],"tags":[9154,8716,8840]}